            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ulpi<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Gaudenti<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> in<lb break="no" n="2"/>conparabili <note>sic</note> filiae <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ensium</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ierum</ex></expan> VIIII Ulpius Part<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="4"/>nopeus et Iulia Sabina <lb n="5"/>parentis <note>sic</note> posue<lb break="no" n="6"/>ru&amp;lt;nt=M&amp;gt; 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten; in mehrere Teile gebrochen; z. T. ergänzt. Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata. Z. 2 (Ende): Buchstabe L in FILIAE fast in Form eines C. Z. 3: D mit Querhaste in der Mitte; dahinter VI-Ligatur. (B): Bulić; CIL III; ILJug: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
